Uses IDs and Classes

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>JS Bin</title>
</head>
<body>
<p>This should have a green background</p>
<p>This too</p>
<p>And this</p>
<hr>
<p>This should have blue background</p>
<p>This too</p>
<p>And this</p>
<hr>
<p>This should be red!</p>
</body>
</html>

####2
Uses IDs and Classes

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>JS Bin</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="block">Text</div>
  <div id="special">Text</div>
<div class="block">Text</div>
<div class="block">Text</div>
</body>
</html>
